  "What is polarization?": "",
  "Polarization restricts light waves to vibrate in a single plane. Polarizing sunglasses block horizontally polarized light (glare from surfaces) while transmitting vertically polarized light. The answer is 'Restricting oscillation of a transverse wave to a single plane'. The other options — 'Increasing the speed of light', 'Changing the color of light', and 'Bending light around obstacles' — are related concepts but do not correctly answer this specific question.": ""
